recipesJson.name: Infected Custard
recipesJson.author: BRDZ
recipesJson.description:
NOTE: WF MILK CARAMEL CANDY = SA MILKY CARAMEL FUDGE
A flavour bomb of ry4 & subtle caramel infected custard, a real treat. I first thought this would be over flavoured but after a 2 week steep it forms an awesomly thick ry4 custard
